{"tid":1989547,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聞8.31 江永祥：死嘅係我腦細胞","createTime":"2020-04-26T05:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T07:19:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"30c9de451384fcd34dade1d01601393bf9bbad7e","tid":1989547,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:11:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200426/M5OTTPT4EJCR4X47YOUCLNLJZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200426%2FM5OTTPT4EJCR4X47YOUCLNLJZE%2F&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnClu%2BYei5PLor89YqF%2FSdhCs%3D&h=1cb6c472\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200426%2FM5OTTPT4EJCR4X47YOUCLNLJZE%2F&h=56c89f9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200426/M5OTTPT4EJCR4X47YOUCLNLJZE/</a><br />\n<br />\n聞8.31 江永祥：死嘅係我腦細胞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方昨日在社交平台Instagram發佈一段長約六分鐘「5秒答問大會」短片，挑選50條早前向網民收集的問題回應。警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥更回應7.21元朗恐襲、七警案、及「一哥」何時落台等較尖銳問題，表示「警隊唔會冇一哥，香港亦唔會冇警隊」。<br />\n<br />\n短片開首是一名手持委任證的女子「琪琪」邊走邊答，包括投考資格、受訓情況等。有網民問到想投考警察，但怕人家目光該怎麼辦，她說：「唔使理人哋，做好自己就可以。」至於外界對警隊有誤解有何感覺，她則稱「吃力不討好」，但會努力消除市民誤解。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200426/large/1587832228_3e8a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200426%2Flarge%2F1587832228_3e8a.gif&h=5a957569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方昨在IG發佈短片，江永祥現身回答8.31有否打死人等尖銳問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民：唔怪得腦殘<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：市民轟郭：讀咁多書學乜<br />\n<br />\n最後四條較尖銳題目由警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥現身解說，被問到何時調查7.21元朗恐襲，他回答從來沒有停止調查，聲稱至今已拘捕37人，當中七人已落案及上庭；問及8.31太子站警察無差別追打市民事件死亡人數及證據，他則回應說：「死咗幾多人？死嘅係我嘅腦細胞呀，俾你哋激死。」<br />\n<br />\n至於會否就七警案向市民道歉，江永祥僅稱警務處處長已經表示會根據公務員守則及警隊條例跟進，秉公辦理。片中主持又問及「一哥」何時下台，江永祥回應說：「處長理直氣壯做得好，只有懼怕我哋正義嘅人，先會想處長辭職。警隊唔會冇一哥，香港亦唔會冇警隊。」<br />\n<br />\n網民留言諷刺，「幾時答點解7.21會同騷（show）械黑社會搭膊」、「又真係死好多腦細胞，唔怪得知腦殘啦」、「我真係多謝你喎，7.21捉到37個」等。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張文鈴"},{"pid":"df7097b3c34ba4b979e7ce6a717a4455278f6a02","tid":1989547,"uid":17641,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"你媽死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9658881a8a7813601874f44d469c4e16e4160c56","tid":1989547,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"我看它腦細胞早就死光了"},{"pid":"94918abdffafbaedf6e1262853ab895a836f32e3","tid":1989547,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:29:04.000Z","msg":"跟大佬去做成龍咪得"},{"pid":"76b08c9bccf9a5b0a7d6ae5552b9f5143cbcdf69","tid":1989547,"uid":120070,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"佢地早已經唔知驚 為所欲為"},{"pid":"cd7f4720a89977c59e0c540b0c6bd2b728578189","tid":1989547,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df7097b3c34ba4b979e7ce6a717a4455278f6a02","tid":1989547,"uid":17641,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"你媽死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"又秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598a36278ff50e013e8a55c4c3fef9fda28f6da4","tid":1989547,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:32:37.000Z","msg":"佢個腦一早賣左比共"},{"pid":"cfd816e59c2766ecdc82e569eb557f452e986a18","tid":1989547,"uid":115847,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OdPCuUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOdPCuUD.jpg&h=7a7ae407&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ae6ad64a636b1e69a9701edc3cace09d39a4197","tid":1989547,"uid":108006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T05:55:17.000Z","msg":"人一藍，腦便殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148b600ed1f333e3fa16f38f1f63d5b4b7f4dc42","tid":1989547,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"無腦何來細胞?<br />\n咁都要講大話"}]}